      "title": "Government employees work from home for another month",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Public Administration, Home Affairs, Provincial Councils and Local Government has issued a new circular allowing employees of government institutions to work from home for another month.",
        "Accordingly, from today (24th), the calling of public servants to work will be restricted for another month."
      ],
